### CardContainer (‚Üí [`components/cards/CardContainer.astro`](mdc:../components/cards/CardContainer.astro))
**The base for ALL cards.** Handles:
- Link wrapping (automatic if href provided)
- Hover states (auto-enabled for links)
- Background icons
- Consistent padding
- Proper semantics

