## üìù Decision Matrix

### "Should I create a component?"
```
Used 3+ times?          ‚Üí YES, create component
Complex state/logic?    ‚Üí YES, create component  
Just styling?          ‚Üí NO, use Tailwind
Variations needed?     ‚Üí YES, create with props
```

### "Where should styles go?"
```
Shared across components?  ‚Üí /styles/components/
Specific to component?     ‚Üí <style> in .astro
Quick prototype?          ‚Üí Tailwind in template
Complex responsive?       ‚Üí SCSS with mixins
```

### "Which spacing to use?"
```
Component padding?     ‚Üí $space-6 (32px)
Section padding?      ‚Üí $space-10 (64px)
Small gaps?          ‚Üí $space-4 (16px)
Micro adjustments?   ‚Üí Tailwind (p-2, m-1)
```

### "Which container to use?"
```
Card grid layout?       ‚Üí container-bordered + cards-grid
Text content?          ‚Üí container-padded
Custom layout?         ‚Üí container-simple + custom padding
```

### "Which section type to use?"
```
Standard content?      ‚Üí section-full
With background grid?  ‚Üí section-grid
Hero section?          ‚Üí Hero component
```

## üîç Quick Debug Checklist

- [ ] Container not centered? ‚Üí Missing `.container` class
- [ ] Borders not showing? ‚Üí Check if < 1450px screen
- [ ] Padding too big on mobile? ‚Üí Use responsive mixins
- [ ] Cards not aligned? ‚Üí Use `.cards-grid`
- [ ] Hover not working? ‚Üí Check `hasHover` prop
- [ ] Text overflowing? ‚Üí Add `TruncateText`
- [ ] Inconsistent spacing? ‚Üí Use py-responsive-md/px-responsive-md classes
- [ ] Card not inheriting styles? ‚Üí Make sure to use CardContainer as base

